The BIM_converter is a standalone rest service running within tomcat.

make "war" by issuing the command:

mvn package -Djava.awt.headless=true

The 'bimconverter.war' will be fount at target/


Change owner of basedir (to enable creation of repoDir):
sudo chown tomcat6.tomcat6 /var/lib/tomcat6


Eclipse: Plugins:
1) subclipse
2) m2eclipse (maven integration)

JDK: Java 6

update 'jsdai_runtime.jar' from upstream (http://...jsdai...)
generate and compile IFC_2x3.jar from either:

1) express compiler + IFC schema from Building Smart
2) jsdai-express eclipse plugin (project , import/copy schema, kompile/generate -> javaclass)
